=== Indications === ==== Bathing ==== * In addition to {{ill|General Indications|ja|一般的適応症|1=General Indications for hot spring use|12=draft}}, these springs are said to help with: ** {{ill|Atherosclerosis|ja|Atherosclerosis|12=draft}}
